metadata.description: the first token from xtractia, a collection of digital abstract artworks resulting from the artist's attempt at extracting the essence of natural beauty and emotional engagement from interactions in the natural realm and during the process of technological transformation recontextualizing those elements for fresh consumption. original non-ai artwork by canadian cryptoartist ejthek [2022]. 3741x3741px png.
